to add a conditional formatting in odoo simply just in the method you have created for the report


def method(self, workbook, data, orders):
   formula1 = workbook.add_format({'':}) #here you can add anything you want including css
   
  formula1 = workbook.add_format({'align':'center'})
    formula1 = workbook.add_format({'num_format':'yyyy-mm-dd'}) this is for date field 






















